      "content": "Sorry to hear that, but maybe not quite. While the RICE method (Rest, Ice, Compression, Elevation) can help alleviate symptoms, ankle sprains can be quite serious and take time to heal. Infractured ligaments or other potential complications may require immediate medical attention. It's best to err on the side of caution and visit a doctor or an urgent care center to get a proper diagnosis and treatment plan.",
